825
00:57:21,105 --> 00:57:22,704
What do you mean?

826
00:57:22,706 --> 00:57:25,607
Well, do you ever have bad thoughts

827
00:57:25,609 --> 00:57:29,545
that you cannot hold inside?

828
00:57:30,113 --> 00:57:31,980
