829
00:57:31,982 --> 00:57:33,215
I'm starting to feel

830
00:57:33,217 --> 00:57:35,651
that you people ought to be ashamed

831
00:57:35,653 --> 00:57:37,553
of asking all these questions

832
00:57:37,555 --> 00:57:39,822
