864
00:59:52,121 --> 00:59:53,822
She did what?

865
00:59:53,824 --> 00:59:55,891
You... you didn't...

866
00:59:56,659 --> 00:59:58,327
No. Don't... don't
get hysterical.

867
00:59:58,329 --> 01:00:01,363
No, you... you're not
