1056
01:19:37,806 --> 01:19:40,474
It's ok to be angry.

1057
01:19:42,844 --> 01:19:44,445
It's ok...

1058
01:19:44,980 --> 01:19:47,148
To be angry.

1059
01:19:59,529 --> 01:20:03,998
