1061
01:20:05,034 --> 01:20:07,468
It's making it worse..

1062
01:20:08,870 --> 01:20:11,338
Stop that.

1063
01:20:17,078 --> 01:20:18,579
Hi.

1064
01:20:20,081 --> 01:20:22,082
Well, hello.

1065
01:20:22,084 --> 01:20:27,454
